###
### Usage: Change the third person xyz via a hotfix, no need to use a cheat table.
###

###
### Special Thanks to apocalyptech, couldn't have done this without him. Someone buy them a beer.
###

# Edit the XYZ at the end of both of these values

SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/GameData/Camera/CameraMode_ThirdPerson.CameraMode_ThirdPerson:CameraBehavior_OffsetCameraRelative_0,LocationOffset,0,,(x=-150,y=25,z=55)

SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/GameData/Camera/CameraMode_ThirdPersonViewModel.CameraMode_ThirdPersonViewModel:CameraBehavior_OffsetCameraRelative_0,LocationOffset,0,,(x=-150,y=25,z=55)
